    "pseudocode":  "FLOW Microflow: SmartExpenses.ACT_Transaction_BulkEditSave\r\nNODES=16; EDGES=15\r\n1. START\r\n2. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve TransactionList over association BulkEditHelper_Transaction from BulkEditHelper\r\n3. LOOP iterate TransactionList as IteratorTransaction\r\n  4. LOOP BODY\r\n    5. ACTION ChangeObjectAction: change IteratorTransaction (Transaction_Balance=if $BulkEditHelper/SmartExpenses.BulkEditHelper_Balance != empty then $BulkEditHelper/SmartExpenses.BulkEditHelper_Balance else $IteratorTransaction/SmartExpenses.Transaction_Balan..., Transaction_BudgetTerm=if $BulkEditHelper/SmartExpenses.BulkEditHelper_BudgetTerm != empty then $BulkEditHelper/SmartExpenses.BulkEditHelper_BudgetTerm else $IteratorTransaction/SmartExpenses.Transaction..., InOut=if $BulkEditHelper/InOut != empty then $BulkEditHelper/InOut else $IteratorTransaction/InOut; refreshInClient=false)\r\n    6. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow SmartExpenses.SUB_Transaction_setStatus\r\n7. ACTION CommitAction: commit TransactionList (refreshInClient=true, withEvents=false)\r\n8. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve Balance over association BulkEditHelper_Balance from BulkEditHelper\r\n9. DECISION Found? expression=$Balance != empty\r\n10. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=true\r\n  11. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow SmartExpenses.SUB_Balance_Recalculate\r\n  12. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n  13. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve BudgetTerm over association BulkEditHelper_BudgetTerm from BulkEditHelper\r\n  14. DECISION BudgetTerm found? expression=$BudgetTerm != empty\r\n  15. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=true\r\n    16. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow SmartExpenses.SUB_BudgetTerm_Recalculate\r\n    17. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n    18. ACTION CloseFormAction: close page\r\n    19. END\r\n  20. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=false\r\n    21. REF ExclusiveMerge\r\n22. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=false\r\n  23. REF ExclusiveMerge",
